The Secretary of State shall furnish the Committee with such information as the Committee may reasonably require for the proper discharge of its functions.\'94
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s1 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 9.\tab}}\pard\plain \s1\qj \li0\ri0\sb240\sa240\widctlpar\jclisttab\tx0\hyphpar0\faauto\ls19\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 
