\par  ... 
\par (b) to section 173 below,
\par where the Secretary of State proposes to make regulations under any of the relevant enactments, he shall refer the proposals, in the form of draft regulations or otherwise, to the Committee.\'94
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s1 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 10.\tab}}\pard\plain \s1\qj \li0\ri0\sb240\sa240\widctlpar\jclisttab\tx0\hyphpar0\faauto\ls19\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 
