(1) Nothing in any enactment shall require any proposals in respect of regulations to be referred to the Committee ... if \endash 
\par }\pard \s24\qj \li1440\ri0\sa240\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1440\itap0 {(a) it appears to the Secretary of State that by reason of the urgency of the matter it is inexpedient so to refer them; or
